# Vir demo
# Regenerate with: vhs demo.tape  (see CONTRIBUTING.md)
Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 75ms

Sleep 1s

Type "vir --help"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 700ms
Type "vir doctor"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 9s

Sleep 2s
